<h2>Bucky Box a low-cost self-service solution</h2>

<p>To make Bucky Box affordable, we follow an open-source, self-service model. While we host the software so it's easy to sign up and use without technical knowledge, <strong>sales support and technical support is not included</strong>. If you need support this will be charged on a per issue basis. You can <a href="http://blog.buckybox.com/2017/07/bucky-box-is-now-open-source-come-to-us-for-hosting-and-support/">read more</a> on our blog.</p>


<p>Thanks for being a local food hero, and welcome to your new account with Bucky Box.</p>

